org.kiji.schema
Class KijiDataWrapper<T>

java.lang.Object
  org.kiji.schema.KijiDataWrapper<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The output data type of wrapped data.
Direct Known Subclasses:
KeyValueBackedWrapper
public abstract class KijiDataWrapper<T>
extends Object

Base class for wrappers of data used in KijiDataWriters.

Data wrappers should be used in conjunction with instances of WrappedDataWriters. Each wrapper should provide functionality to wrap an individual data element through the wrap(EntityId, String, String, Schema, long, Object) method and wrap multiple elements using the add(EntityId, String, String, Schema, long, Object) and getWrapped() methods.
